(15866, 'sectors_4_sector_facts_1_fact', '\r\nCentre Hospitalier de l’Université de Montréal, Canada – As one of the world’s largest healthcare projects , the CAD$2.1bn deal represents the most valuable social infrastructure PPP scheme in Canada’s history. - See more at: http://www.laingorourke.com/our-work/our-sectors/buildings.aspx#sthash.ok4wIKcV.dpuf', 'yes'),
