(64, 1, '2015-06-18 06:20:30', '2015-06-18 06:20:30', '<p class="lead">Haven Inn contracted Omega Industries to undertake the internal and external painting works for a refurbishment project based in Glebe (NSW).</p>\r\n<p>Omega were chosen to complete the project based on previous recommendation and merit of restructuring workflows for efficiency, cost reduction and safety without compromising on workmanship quality.</p>\r\n\r\nDulux were the specified brand for this project. Products included Dulux Professional Total Prep, Dulux Professional Range and Dulux Weathershield.', 'Haven Inn Glebe', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'portfolio-title-5', '', '', '2015-09-23 12:32:15', '2015-09-23 12:32:15', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Omega/php/?post_type=portfolios&#038;p=64', 0, 'portfolios', '', 0),
(65, 1, '2015-06-18 06:21:01', '2015-06-18 06:21:01', '<p class="lead">Omega Industries are the preferred line marking services provider to Beaumont Tiles since 2015. Works are related to the restructuring and maintenance of their line marking areas for various distribution warehouses in NSW.</p>\r\nBeaumont Tiles is Australia''s leading tile distributor for the consumer, building and renovator sector. A requirement for easy access to an extensive range of tile products in large warehouses (&gt;7000 sqm) is essential for smooth function of their operations.\r\n\r\nOmega is a key service partner in the planning and implementation of warehouse line marking designs and implementation to ensure the best possible outcome for logistics aspects are met.', 'Beaumont Tiles', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'portfolio-title-6', '', '', '2015-09-23 11:53:36', '2015-09-23 11:53:36', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Omega/php/?post_type=portfolios&#038;p=65', 0, 'portfolios', '', 0),
