(191, 1, '2015-08-18 00:23:48', '2015-08-18 00:23:48', '<h1>Award Winning Industrial Painters</h1>\r\n<h3>(MPA 2014 Best Industrial Project)</h3>\r\nAt Omega Industries, specialised industrial painting is at the very crux of our business. Industrial painting in itself requires a combination of technical and practical abilities coupled with an an extremely proficient team of experienced industrial painters. Omega have the necessary skills and qualifications to undertake any kind of industrial work on either minor work or major project scales. The Omega team also always endeavour to complete painting services on time AND on budget.\r\n<h2>What do our industrial painting services involve?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Dependable results that last for years.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Protective coating</strong> for steel surfaces and equipment.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sodablasting and respraying,</strong> for non-destructive restoration. This is ideal for graffiti removal or paint-stripping sensitive surfaces.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Expert painters</strong> who are experienced with paint application in all types of interior and exterior industrial spaces – confined spaces, vaulted ceilings and multi-storey buildings are no problem for us.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Metal surface restoration and coatings,</strong> for railings and industrial equipment refurbishment.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Private or public car park line markings,</strong> for safety and access signage.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Fast response fire damage and vandalism restoration repainting</strong> and repairs.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Waste management to EPA standards</strong> and site clean-up.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Pressure cleaning and dirt removal,</strong> as maintenance or to prepare properties for sale.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>A high regard for safety.</strong> This also extends to our specialised safety equipment.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Concrete grinding and sealing</strong> of building exteriors and floors.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Epoxy floor coatings</strong> for standardising warehouse flooring.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Rust treatment and re-coating</strong> of industrial equipment for railings and banisters.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sandblasting and restoration</strong> of industrial infrastructure, such as electrical transformers.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Public building repainting</strong> and maintenance.</li>\r\n	<li>Very high standard of paint finishing.</li>\r\n	<li>We also provide <strong>council approval services</strong>, traffic management services and other miscellaneous public safety services</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 style="color: #000000; text-align: justify;">Why Omega Industries?</h4>\r\nIf you’re after a professional industrial painting service that consistently delivers, we can help. Feel free to visit our <a title="Projects" href="http://supplyandapply.com.au/commercial/projects/">projects page </a>for details on the many different industrial painting services our team has already carried out. If, however, you have any questions, don’t hesitate to give us a call on 1300 372 468 or, alternatively, fill out our online contact form.', 'Industrial Painting', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'research-development', '', '', '2015-09-28 03:34:42', '2015-09-28 03:34:42', '', 179, 'http://111.93.163.213/Omega/php/?page_id=191', 0, 'page', '', 0),
