(344, 1, '2015-09-23 12:12:51', '2015-09-23 12:12:51', '<p class="lead">FPM Milling contracted Omega Industries to undertake the pressure cleaning, abrasive blasting and application of a premium polyurethane system to their silos in Tamworth (Regional NSW).</p>\r\n<p>In order to avoid heavy financial implications in the future FPM assets required coatings removal, cleaning and application. The opportunity presented itself when an Omega project manager took a wrong turn on his way to inspect works at the Tamworth Court House project. Instead came across silos and areas of a cereal milling plant that needed attention.</p>\r\n\r\nWorks required our industrial crew to complete abrasive blasting, high reach access using EWP and repainting areas with a Omethane Two Pack Polyurethane 343. The the completed project met with specification parameters and approved by our technical team in Sydney.', 'FPM Cereal Milling', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '61-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-23 12:12:51', '2015-09-23 12:12:51', '', 61, 'http://111.93.163.213/Omega/php/61-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
