(357, 1, '2015-09-01 06:13:29', '2015-09-01 06:13:29', '<p class="lead">Omega Industries are the preferred line marking services provider to Beaumont Tiles since 2015. Works are related to the restructuring and maintenance of their line marking areas for various distribution warehouses in NSW.</p>\nBeaumont Tiles is Australia''s leading tile distributor for the consumer, building and renovator sector. A requirement for easy access to an extensive range of tile products in large warehouses (&gt;7000 sqm) is essential for smooth function of teir operations.\n\nOmega is a key service partner in the planning and implementation of warehouse line marking designs and implementation to ensure the best possible outcome for logistics aspects are met.', 'Beaumont Tiles', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '65-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-01 06:13:29', '2015-09-01 06:13:29', '', 65, 'http://111.93.163.213/Omega/php/65-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(358, 1, '2015-09-01 06:27:57', '2015-09-01 06:27:57', 'Apco Coatings is a leading paint company manufacting architectural, industrial and the largest Australian road marking paint manufacturer.\n\n&nbsp;\n<p class="bottom_spacer">Apco Coatings, the fast growing paint company in the South Pacific belongs to a large world wide group of the best paint companies. The figures are hard to beat; operations in 20 countries, a turnover of over US$ 1 billion and a ranking in the worlds top ten decorative paint brands.</p>\n<p class="bottom_spacer">The story begins with India''s premier paint manufacturer, Asian Paints, its 60 year pedigree has seen the company named as one of the top six best managed companies in the country.</p>\n<p class="bottom_spacer">Asian Paints as a company operates in 20 countries across the world. It has manufacturing facilities in each of these countries and is the largest paint company in nine overseas markets. Asian Paints operates in five regions across the world viz. South Asia, South East Asia, South Pacific, Middle East and Caribbean region through the four corporate brands viz. Asian Paints, Berger International, SCIB Paints and Apco Coatings.</p>\n<p class="bottom_spacer">International expansion to the South Pacific began in 1977. This has now resulted in operations though subsidiaries in Fiji Islands, New Zealand, Samoa, Solomon Islands, Tonga, Vanuatu and a technological tie-up with Apco Coatings, Australia.</p>\n<p class="bottom_spacer">Global alliances give Apco Coatings a head start with technical collaboration, The research and development department is one of the largest in the Asia Pacific region leading to the most advanced, innovative product portfolio and exciting, contemporary painting options offering.</p>', 'Apco Coatings', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '195-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-01 06:27:57', '2015-09-01 06:27:57', '', 195, 'http://111.93.163.213/Omega/php/195-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
