faces.</li>\n\n	<li>Spray or brush hot plastics or pitch onto surfaces.</li>\n\n	<li>Bake finishes on painted or enameled articles, using baking ovens.</li>\n\n</ul>\n', 'Painter', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '493-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-24 03:00:18', '2015-09-24 03:00:18', '', 493, 'http://111.93.163.213/Omega/php/493-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
