(522, 1, '2015-09-24 04:29:48', '2015-09-24 04:29:48', 'Callum was appointed Group Commercial Director in November 2014, and prior to this was Director of Finance and Commerce from April 2013. He is responsible for the Group’s commercial function, as well as supporting business development and Group strategy formulation. He is a member of the Group Executive Committee and several of its subcommittees\r\nCallum joined the Group with the acquisition of Laing Construction by R O’Rourke & Son in 2001, having worked for the Laing business since 1992. His previous roles include Managing Director of Laing O’Rourke Construction UK, Commercial Services Director for Europe as well as Commercial Director for Laing O’Rourke’s Middle East and South Asia portfolio of businesses from 2006 to 2009.\r\nCallum is a Chartered Quantity Surveyor and was an inaugural member of the Young Guns programme for high-potential leaders in 2003 and subsequently the Guns senior leadership programme in 2008.\r\n- See more at: http://www.laingorourke.com/who-we-are/leadership.aspx#sthash.TglFffQ2.dpuf', 'Callum Tuckett', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'callum-tuckett', '', '', '2015-09-24 04:29:48', '2015-09-24 04:29:48', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Omega/php/?post_type=leaderships&#038;p=522', 0, 'leaderships', '', 0),
