(537, 1, '2015-09-24 06:05:07', '2015-09-24 06:05:07', '<div id="intro"><p>An alliance featuring Laing O''Rourke has begun the construction of Perth''s newest transport link - See more at: http://www.laingorourke.com/media/news-releases/2015/stadium-station-kicks-off.aspx#sthash.AkTaqWJc.dpufases.</p><div>\r\nAn alliance featuring Laing O''Rourke has begun the construction of Perth''s newest transport link\r\nPerth Stadium Station Transport Minister Dean Nalder on site\r\n\r\nWest Australian Transport Minister, the Hon. Dean Nalder MLA, last week visited Perth''s Stadium Station site to officially launch the first construction works.\r\n\r\nBeing delivered by an alliance of Laing O''Rourke, AECOM and the Public Transport Authority, the project will transform the Burswood precinct and deliver the city''s second-largest transport interchange.\r\n- See more at: http://www.laingorourke.com/media/news-releases/2015/stadium-station-kicks-off.aspx#sthash.AkTaqWJc.dpuf', 'Stadium Station kicks off', 'An alliance featuring Laing O''Rourke has begun the construction of Perth''s newest transport link - See more at: http://www.laingorourke.com/media/news-releases/2015/stadium-station-kicks-off.aspx#sthash.AkTaqWJc.dpufases.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'stadium-station-kicks-off', '', '', '2015-09-28 01:44:12', '2015-09-28 01:44:12', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Omega/php/?post_type=news&#038;p=537', 0, 'news', '', 0),
