(541, 1, '2015-09-24 06:34:31', '2015-09-24 06:34:31', 'Overview Our collaborative approach through early design involvement, engineering expertise and integrated delivery ensures we are able to complete complex projects to exacting time, cost and quality standards, safely and sustainably. Across key business sectors we design, procure, manage, construct, refurbish and maintain commercial offices, data centres, industrial facilities and science and research centres. Lifestyle and Leisure We provide engineering, construction, project management and operational maintenance services for Lifestyle markets covering hotels, residential, retail, sports and leisure in Europe, Middle East and Australia. Many developments – such as sporting stadia or convention centres – attract intense public scrutiny. Clients need to know they are working with a partner who will protect their reputation through flawless delivery to often immovable deadlines. We understand the multiple functions these facilities have to serve and we apply our in-depth knowledge of complex sports and multi-purpose venues to maximise return on the clients’ investments. We have delivered some of the world’s most iconic lifestyle complexes, such as the Atlantis Hotel in Dubai, the convention centres of Brisbane, the Gold Coast, Darwin and Hong Kong. We were the lead member of the consortium managing delivery of major elements of the London 2012 Olympic and Paralympic Park,…', 'Building & Construction', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'building-construction', '', '', '2015-09-28 03:56:28', '2015-09-28 03:56:28', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Omega/php/?p=541', 46, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
