(568, 1, '2015-09-28 03:25:14', '2015-09-28 03:25:14', '<div id="mainContent">\r\n    <article>\r\n        <div id="intro"><p>Laing O’Rourke operates through two major geographic hubs, Europe and Australia. Our European operations span Abu Dhabi, Canada, Dubai and the United Kingdom. Our Australian operations cover Australia, Hong Kong, New Zealand and South East Asia.&nbsp;</p></div><p><br>\r\n</p><div id="globalStaticMap"><img width="700" height="450" alt="" src="/~/media/lor/images/diagrams-and-maps/where-we-work-map-201_v4.jpg?h=450&amp;la=en&amp;mw=700&amp;w=700"></div><div class="twoCols"><div class="col"><h2>Europe</h2><p class="colIntro">Our European Hub comprises Laing O’Rourke’s operations in key building and infrastructure sectors and construction markets and has valuable relationships with prestigious client organisations.</p><p>The Group is one of the leading construction solution providers in our chosen sectors. Our aim is to leverage the scale and efficiencies of our vertically integrated delivery business to generate profitable revenues in our core markets and collaborating with like-minded partners. We will complement this approach by building leading positions in selective growth-orientated sectors and territories with the right strategic and cultural fit.</p></div><div class="col"><h2>Australia</h2><p class="colIntro">Laing O’Rourke has been active in Australia since 2004 and is now integrating the global capabilities of the wider Group to provide a distinctive proposition based on superior quality of design, delivery and service.</p><p>We are growing a diversified project portfolio by taking leading positions in carefully targeted sectors and markets. These are predominantly in building and social infrastructure, mining and minerals handing, oil &amp; gas, rail and power where demand is being driven by the emerging world economic superpowers in and around the region.</p></div></div><div class="pulloutFigures"><div class="row"><span class="figures left">£5.6bn</span><span class="desc"><span>Value of order book (end of March 2013)</span></span><span class="figures right">$2.6bn</span></div><div class="row"><span class="figures left">11,208</span><span class="desc"><span>Number of employees (end of March 2013)</span></span><span class="figures right">4,143</span></div></div><div class="clearfix" id="socialNetworkingWrapper"><div class="socialNetworkingContainer" id="facebookLike"><div id="fb-root" class=" fb_reset"><div style="position: absolute; top: -10000px; height: 0px; width: 0px;"><div><iframe frameborder="0" name="fb_xdm_frame_http" allowtransparency="true" allowfullscreen="true" scrolling="no" id="fb_xdm_frame_http" aria-hidden="true" title="Facebook Cross Domain Communication Frame" tabindex="-1" style="border: medium none;" src="http://static.ak.facebook.com/connect/xd_arbiter/6brUqVNoWO3.js?version=41#channel=f257db90b4a7aa4&amp;origin=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.laingorourke.com"></iframe><iframe frameborder="0" name="fb_xdm_frame_https" allowtransparency="true" allowfullscreen="true" scrolling="no" id="fb_xdm_frame_https" aria-hidden="true" title="Facebook Cross Domain Communication Frame" tabindex="-1" style="border: medium none;" src="https://s-static.ak.facebook.com/connect/xd_arbiter/6brUqVNoWO3.js?version=41#channel=f257db90b4a7aa4&amp;origin=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.laingorourke.com"></iframe></div></div></div><script>\r\n          (function (d, s, id) {\r\n          var js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];\r\n          if (d.getElementById(id)) { return; }\r\n          js = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;\r\n          js.src = "//connect.facebook.net/en_US/all.js#xfbml=1";\r\n          fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);\r\n          } (document, ''script'', ''facebook-jssdk''));\r\n\r\n        </script><div data-show-faces="false" data-width="100" data-send="false" data-layout="button_count" class="fb-like"></div></div><div class="socialNetworkingContainer" id="twitterButton"><a class="twitter-share-but